# Model Selection (quick reference)

> **Canonical policy:** `.cursor/rules/agent-routing.mdc` (always applied)

| Tier | Use for | Never for |
|---|---|---|
| **Composer** | Terminal, logs, cache, dev server, git status, health checks | Migrations, auth, business logic, multi-file code |
| **Sonnet** | Features, bugs, refactors, migrations, UI, server actions | Pure terminal tasks |
| **Opus** | Architecture audit, security/RLS review, critical design forks | Routine coding, commands |

Default: **Sonnet**. Opus only when deep system judgment is the deliverable.
